"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-09-athlete-turned-entrepreneur-launches-jamaica-leisure-wear-ahead-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A former athlete, Fernando Edwards always finds time to watch the sports, especially major meets like the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Paris Games two weeks away, the Jamaican entrepreneur has launched a line of patriotic leisure wear.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 157, \"end\": 165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999039052169195, \"rank\": 9.610083343951852e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The T-shirts, which bear images of Jamaica's athletes as well as colours of the country's flag, are manufactured by Jamroc Dept, a company Edwards operates in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999899904642742, \"rank\": 9.790815771109434e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999788696292993, \"rank\": 2.0736226814400408e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came up with these designs in February.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew the Olympics were approaching and I wanted to give the fans a way to show that they are in support of Team Jamaica.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether they are Jamaican or not, this line will let everyone know who they are rooting for,\\\" he toldObserver Online.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To help expose his line, Edwards plans to approach popular personalities to endorse the product which he personally designed.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A model wearing patriotic Jamaica leisure wear manufactured by Jamroc Dept.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999899904642742, \"rank\": 9.790815771109434e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in Clarendon, Edwards competed over 200 and 400 metres for Bridgeport High School at the 2004 and 2005 Boys Championship.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Layshia_Clarendon\", \"score\": 0.9999998788594058, \"rank\": 5.906025707434553e-08, \"text\": \"Clarendon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Layshia_Clarendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Layshia_Clarendon\"}, {\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bridgeport,_Texas\", \"score\": 0.6869220607011223, \"rank\": 0.22499999999997466, \"text\": \"Bridgeport High School\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bridgeport,_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bridgeport,_Texas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also represented that school at the 2005 Penn Relays.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He received a track scholarship to Missouri Baptist University, competing for that institution in the National Association of Intercollegiate Athletics over 200 and 400 metres.\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Missouri\", \"score\": 0.8103002446381552, \"rank\": 0.20921096473836295, \"text\": \"Missouri\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Missouri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Missouri\"}, {\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri_Baptist_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Missouri Baptist University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri_Baptist_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri_Baptist_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympics (July 26-April 11) approached, Edwards was determined to not only salute the current Jamaican team, but honour his country's remarkable athletics history.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999039052169195, \"rank\": 9.610083343951852e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to do something creative and different from the larger brands, that actually represents us and is by us.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a bigger goal to give back to Jamaica, and track and field is a big sport for our culture that can help bring awareness to the brand,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1576, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999899904642742, \"rank\": 9.790815771109434e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A model wearing patriotic Jamaica leisure wear manufactured by Jamroc Dept.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999899904642742, \"rank\": 9.790815771109434e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards gave up athletics after graduating from Missouri Baptist University, where he earned a degree in business management.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri_Baptist_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Missouri Baptist University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri_Baptist_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missouri_Baptist_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Missouri\", \"score\": 0.8103002446381552, \"rank\": 0.20921096473836295, \"text\": \"Missouri\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Missouri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Missouri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He moved to Los Angeles, starting a catering business and becoming an actor/director in projects such as the 2023 crime thriller, Rooted Betrayal.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 2045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1911, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999788696292993, \"rank\": 2.0736226814400408e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2036, \"end\": 2044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betrayal\", \"score\": 0.9999999372528257, \"rank\": 6.274722819738044e-08, \"text\": \"Betrayal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betrayal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betrayal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": []}]}"